hey can't make their own storyline up...My girlfriend isn't really all into gaming, but I wanted to be with her online and offline...)</P><P>Anyways, I hope someone repiles...thanks!!!!!!!!</P><P></P><P></P><P>To be, or not to be...<BR>...What was the question again?</font></td>
